706704f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sheepshead Bay Road - Avenue X
706704f-a.text:
1151-1153 Sheepshead Bay Road, at the N.E. corner of Ave. K. In
1916 the 2-story house was No. 69. In 1873 the Catholic Church of Sheeps-
head Bay was on the west side of the intersection of Sheepshead Bay Road and
Stuart Street. At some subsequent date, it was at the above location.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
